<br>
But, as I understand it, in order for that to work on say something like making FS Bp's or Dishes, you'd have to fill those bags with the appropriate number of molds/Ceramic linings (neither of which stack) and then manually run through making  the items using each of the unstacked molds/sketches in order for the mouse simulator to record the co-ordinates for the macro to use.<br>
